Software Heritage Acquisition Process Guidelines
------------------------------------------------

This directory contains the full sources of the SWHAP Guidelines, in Markdown format.
In order to produce the PDF output, you need the following tools installed:

Mandatory:
 - pandoc https://pandoc.org

Optional:
 - rubber https://launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/rubber

See the Makefile for the commands used to produce LaTeX from Markdown.
